title Sequence – HotelClient Adapter Pattern (huidige JSON → JSON mapping)

participant Main
participant HotelController
participant HotelAdapter
participant "Booking.com API"

Main -> HotelController : GET /hotels?lat=..&long=..&amount=..
HotelController -> HotelAdapter : fetchHotels(lat, long, amount)
HotelAdapter -> "Booking.com API" : HTTP GET request
"Booking.com API" --> HotelAdapter : JSON response
HotelAdapter -> HotelAdapter : map naar interne JSON array
HotelAdapter --> HotelController : JSONArray (intern formaat)
HotelController --> Main : JSON response

@enduml